Texts.Chs: 我相信，这是一幅描绘人类海盗的画作，背景设定在人类历史的古代。
Texts.Eng: A painting of a Human pirate set in the archaic period of Human history, I believe.

Texts.Chs: 一位戴眼罩的人类的画像。
Texts.Eng: A painting of a Human with an eyepatch.

Texts.Chs: 一张奇怪的照片，一个人类穿着奇怪的服装，站在热带海景中。
Texts.Eng: An oddly done picture of a Human in strange costume, standing in a tropical seascape.

Texts.Chs: 我会很难找到人来销赃这件.... 艺术品。
Texts.Eng: I will be hard pressed looking for someone to fence this .... artwork.
Its reputation precedes its very presence!

Texts.Chs: 我的亲和力量揭示了这幅奴隶涂抹中隐藏的一个秘密锁触机制。
Texts.Eng: My Force affinity has revealed a secret lock-and-trigger mechanism secreted in this grotthu daub.

Texts.Chs: 我的内部扫描仪检测到嵌入在这幅画中的高度复杂的遥测和信号组件。
Texts.Eng: My internal scanner detects highly sophisticated telemetric and signalliing components embedded in this painting.

Texts.Chs: 对于一场星际探索游戏来说，这相当离奇和不合时宜，对吧？
Texts.Eng: Pretty quaint and anachronistic for an intergalactic space exploration game, right?

Texts.Chs: 一些早已被遗忘在人类历史之中的人物。也许是迦太基的继承人？
Texts.Eng: Some long forgotten figure from Human history. Perhaps it's the Heir of Carthage?

Texts.Chs: 奇奇奇奇怪的画像出出出出奇的笨重。
奇怪的绘画。用途未知。要使用它干啥？
Texts.Eng: Strange painting. Use unknown. Use it?

Texts.Chs: 只要便宜，就能吸引眼球，这是张陈腐而明显大规模生产的绘画。
Texts.Eng: There is more that meets the eye as far as this cheap, trite and clearly mass-produced painting is concerned.

Texts.Chs: 这幅画一定是盗版的，但看起来很像盗版的。也很奇怪。但是为什么呢？
Texts.Eng: This painting looks piratical as much as it must've been pirated. As well as being odd. But why?

Texts.Chs: 不管这家伙是谁，他似乎少了一只眼睛！
Texts.Eng: Whoever this dude is, he seems to be an eye short!

Texts.Chs: 为什么这个人类被描绘成穿着俗世的服装？这说不通啊。
Texts.Eng: Why is this Human depicted in Grounded costume? that doesn't make any sense.
